Package com.googlecode.cqengine.resultset.common

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CostCachingResultSet<O>
    Caches the merge cost and retrieval costs of a wrapped result set.
    IteratorCachingResultSet<O>
    A ResultSet which wraps a backing ResultSet, and which caches the iterator returned by the backing ResultSet, to enable repeated invocations on IteratorCachingResultSet.iterator().hasNext(), to avoid each time requesting a new iterator from the backing ResultSet.
    QueryCostComparators
    Stateless comparator singletons for ResultSets based on ResultSet.getRetrievalCost() and ResultSet.getMergeCost().
    ResultSets
    Utility methods for working with ResultSet objects.
    WrappedResultSet<O>
    A ResultSet which wraps another.
